org.apache.reef.tang.formats

Class ConfigurationModule

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.reef.tang.formats.ConfigurationModule

  • public class ConfigurationModule
extends Object
    Allows applications to bundle sets of configuration options together into discrete packages. Unlike more conventional approaches, ConfigurationModules store such information in static data structures that can be statically discovered and sanity-checked.
    See Also:
    for more information and examples.
